<h2 style='color: #6B1F2E;'>Payment Receipt</h2>

<p>Dear {{clientName}},</p>

<p>Thank you for your payment to Vasquez Law Firm. This email serves as your official receipt.</p>

<div style='background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;'>
  <h3 style='color: #6B1F2E; margin-top: 0;'>Payment Details</h3>
  <table style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;'>
    <tr>
      <td style='padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;'>Amount Paid:</td>
      <td style='padding: 8px 0; font-size: 18px; color: #6B1F2E;'>{{formatCurrency amount}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style='padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;'>Payment Date:</td>
      <td style='padding: 8px 0;'>{{formatDate date}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style='padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;'>Transaction ID:</td>
      <td style='padding: 8px 0; font-family: monospace;'>{{transactionId}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{#if reference}}
      <tr>
        <td style='padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;'>Reference Number:</td>
        <td style='padding: 8px 0;'>{{reference}}</td>
      </tr>
    {{/if}}
    <tr>
      <td style='padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;'>Description:</td>
      <td style='padding: 8px 0;'>{{description}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{#if caseNumber}}
      <tr>
        <td style='padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;'>Case Number:</td>
        <td style='padding: 8px 0;'>{{caseNumber}}</td>
      </tr>
    {{/if}}
    <tr>
      <td style='padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;'>Payment Method:</td>
      <td style='padding: 8px 0;'>{{gateway}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>

{{#if trustAccount}}
  <div
    style='background-color: #d4edda; border: 1px solid #c3e6cb; color: #155724; padding: 12px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;'
  >
    <strong>Trust Account Deposit</strong><br />
    This payment has been deposited into our trust account in accordance with North Carolina State
    Bar rules. These funds will be held in trust and applied to your legal fees as they are earned.
  </div>
{{/if}}

<h3 style='color: #6B1F2E;'>Important Information</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Please keep this receipt for your records</li>
  <li>This payment will appear on your statement as "VASQUEZ LAW FIRM"</li>
  <li>You can view your payment history in your <a href='{{portalUrl}}'>client portal</a></li>
</ul>

<p style='text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;'>
  <a
    href='javascript:window.print()'
    class='button'
    style='background-color: #C9974D; color: white; padding: 10px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; margin-right: 10px;'
  >Print Receipt</a>
  <a
    href='{{portalUrl}}/payments'
    class='button'
    style='background-color: #6B1F2E; color: white; padding: 10px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;'
  >View Account</a>
</p>

<h3 style='color: #6B1F2E;'>Questions About Your Payment?</h3>
<p>If you have any questions about this payment or need additional documentation, please contact our
  billing department:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Phone: <strong>1-844-967-3536</strong></li>
  <li>Email: <a href='mailto:billing@vasquezlawnc.com'>billing@vasquezlawnc.com</a></li>
</ul>

<p>Thank you for choosing Vasquez Law Firm.</p>

<p>Sincerely,<br />
  <strong>Billing Department</strong><br />
  Vasquez Law Firm</p>

<hr style='border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; margin: 30px 0;' />

<p style='font-size: 12px; color: #666; text-align: center;'>
  This is an automated receipt. Please do not reply directly to this email.<br />
  Vasquez Law Firm, PLLC | Tax ID: XX-XXXXXXX
</p>